<!-- ════════════════ 05 · PLAN VAN AANPAK ════════════════ -->
  <section data-label="Plan van aanpak" class="slide light">
    <div class="glow soft"></div>
    <div class="frame">
      <p class="eyebrow"><span class="num">04</span>Ons plan van aanpak</p>
      <h2 class="h2">Van idee tot resultaat <span class="accent">in 5 stappen</span>.</h2>

      <div class="steps" style="margin-top: 36px; align-content: start; position: relative; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);">

        <div class="step" style="--c: #00d8ff;">
          <div class="step-head">
            <span class="step-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"/><path d="M11 8v6M8 11h6"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="big-n">01</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Smart Scan</h4>
          <p>Processen en knelpunten in kaart. Waar maakt AI écht het verschil?</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step" style="--c: #8b5cf6;">
          <div class="step-head">
            <span class="step-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="big-n">02</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Ontwerp</h4>
          <p>Een aanpak op maat: workflows, agents, automatisaties en integraties met de meeste impact.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step" style="--c: #4f6cf7;">
          <div class="step-head">
            <span class="step-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="big-n">03</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Ontwikkeling</h4>
          <p>Bouwen en testen, stap voor stap. U volgt mee en ziet snel wat werkt.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step" style="--c: #f59e0b;">
          <div class="step-head">
            <span class="step-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z"/><path d="m12 15-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z"/><path d="M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0"/><path d="M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="big-n">04</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Implementatie</h4>
          <p>Alles in uw omgeving, vlot aangesloten op bestaande systemen en werkwijze.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step" style="--c: #10b981;">
          <div class="step-head">
            <span class="step-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 7 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 2 17"/><polyline points="16 7 22 7 22 13"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="big-n">05</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Optimalisatie &amp; support</h4>
          <p>Blijvend bijsturen en uitbreiden, zodat resultaat blijft groeien.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="callout">
        Voor KBC verankeren we deze aanpak in uw <strong>bestaande SDLC, security- en governanceprocessen</strong>. Geen parallelle schaduw-IT, wél versnelling binnen uw kaders.
      </div>
    </div>
    {% set slideNumber = "05" %}
    {% set slideTotal = "15" %}
    {% include "../../shared/chrome.njk" %}
  </section>
